<heading id="A5317A4CFFF3FFA9FF6875C8DAC1FE8C" box="[227,697,239,271]" centered="true" fontSize="12" level="2" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" reason="2">
3.4. Genus 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FEE575C8DAC1FE8C" authority="PACE, 2013" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2013" box="[366,697,239,271]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Rabdotodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FEE575C8DA54FE8C" box="[366,556,239,271]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">Rabdotodrusilla</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF3FFA9FDB875C8DAC1FE8C" author="PACE, R." box="[563,697,239,271]" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" pagination="33 - 63" refId="ref78152" refString="PACE, R. 2013: New distributional data, new species and three new genera of Aleocharinae from Malaysia, Vietnam and Taiwan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Tropical Zoology 26 (1): 33 - 63." type="journal article" year="2013">PACE, 2013</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="B6DC9EABFFF3FFA9FF36740ED9C4FC81" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FFF3FFA9FF36740ED9C4FC81" blockId="66.[189,796,297,770]" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FF36740ED91FFEC2" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2013" box="[189,359,297,321]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Rabdotodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FF36740ED91FFEC2" box="[189,359,297,321]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">Rabdotodrusilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described in the same article as 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FF36746ED923FEE2" authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2016" box="[189,347,329,353]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Episkiodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FF36746ED923FEE2" box="[189,347,329,353]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">Episkiodrusilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The genus previously included only one species, 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FEC1744DDA15FE02" authority="PACE, 2013" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2013" box="[330,621,361,385]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Rabdotodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malaysiensis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FEC1744DD993FE02" box="[330,491,361,385]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">R. malaysiensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF3FFA9FE78744EDA15FE02" author="PACE, R." box="[499,621,361,385]" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" pagination="33 - 63" refId="ref78152" refString="PACE, R. 2013: New distributional data, new species and three new genera of Aleocharinae from Malaysia, Vietnam and Taiwan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Tropical Zoology 26 (1): 33 - 63." type="journal article" year="2013">PACE, 2013</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF3FFA9FD38744EDB6DFE02" box="[691,789,361,385]" name="Malaysia" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
, a species described based on a single female. According to 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF3FFA9FE9A748ED9E7FE42" author="PACE, R." box="[273,415,425,449]" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" pagination="33 - 63" refId="ref78152" refString="PACE, R. 2013: New distributional data, new species and three new genera of Aleocharinae from Malaysia, Vietnam and Taiwan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Tropical Zoology 26 (1): 33 - 63." type="journal article" year="2013">PACE (2013)</bibRefCitation>
, this genus is characterized and distinguished from 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FE1C74EED996FE62" authorityName="LEACH" authorityYear="1819" box="[407,494,457,481]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FE1C74EED996FE62" box="[407,494,457,481]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">Drusilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by a pronotum “with long strong sulci, without a deep median sulcus”. Additional characters are neither indicated nor described. The new species described below is tentatively attributed to 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FF69776ED9F4FDE2" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2013" box="[226,396,585,609]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Rabdotodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FF69776ED9F4FDE2" box="[226,396,585,609]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">Rabdotodrusilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as it shares with 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FDFC776DDB62FDE2" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2013" box="[631,794,585,609]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Rabdotodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malaysiensis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FDFC776DDB62FDE2" box="[631,794,585,609]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">R. malaysiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
the modified sculpture of the pronotum. However, the status of this genus requires revision. The morphology of the aedeagus and other characters suggest that these species belong to 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FE0977EED9A1FD62" authorityName="LEACH" authorityYear="1819" box="[386,473,713,737]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FE0977EED9A1FD62" box="[386,473,713,737]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">Drusilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and that 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF3FFA9FDCF77EEDA96FD62" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2013" box="[580,750,713,737]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Rabdotodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF3FFA9FDCF77EEDA96FD62" box="[580,750,713,737]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="79">Rabdotodrusilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a synonym of that genus.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
